const scriptURL = 'https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbyEMhxVdAiMUJ0SKTER6BYz0mPwCa4DlEeprEfmZNWiYUIGOwrNpEbLi6g8S5eTO7eyPA/exechttps://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbyEMhxVdAiMUJ0SKTER6BYz0mPwCa4DlEeprEfmZNWiYUIGOwrNpEbLi6g8S5eTO7eyPA/exec'
             const form = document.forms['google-sheet']
           
             form.addEventListener('submit', e => {
               e.preventDefault()
               fetch(scriptURL, { method: 'POST', body: new FormData(form)})
                 .then(response => alert("Thanks for Booking Seat..! We Will Contact You Soon..."))
                 .catch(error => console.error('Error!', error.message))
             })
